Marie Déa https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marie_D%C3%A9a 0 Marie Déa (born Odette Alice Marie Deupès 17 May 1912 – 1 March 1992) was a French actress. She appeared in more than fifty films from 1939 to 1983. She was married to the actor Lucien Nat. Marie_Déa ( born Odette_Alice_Marie_Deupès_17_May_1912 – 1_March_1992 ) was a_French_actress .
